# Banner Component with Tailwind CSS & React

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates how to build a **Banner component** in React using **Tailwind CSS**.  
The banner includes:
- A background image
- A gradient overlay
- Centered text content

It is designed to be responsive, clean, and easy to customize.

---

## 🚀 Features
- **Background Image Support**: Uses imported assets or public paths.
- **Gradient Overlay**: Smooth gradient applied on top of the image.
- **Responsive Layout**: Works across different screen sizes.
- **Customizable Content**: Easily replace text or add buttons.

---

